This is a server for large organizations. 
By using this server, we can reduce the amount of internet usage by ensuring that there is no continuous supply of internet.

I have a file that I want to share with others.
I've uploaded it to a server and provided the IP address and port. 
To access the file, just connect to the same network and request the file from the hosted IP address and port.
The maximum file size in the program is 100 GB. This value can be modified.

The software company knows the speed and load on the internet, which it refers to as speed of the software loading.
It depends on the future as the speed of the software loading speed.
This is a personalized software program that works like ShareIt on a mobile app. With further modifications, it can be connected to any type of operating system, since it works on a browser.
